I'm on a break.
I deserve it - I've been working solidly
through lunchtime.

rows.label: tlk44500188_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'd like to retire, but there's work to
be done and I need the money to eat.

rows.label: tlk44500188_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There's nothing to be done about it
as long as this country's closed off...

rows.label: tlk44500188_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's grown old and stagnant...sort of
like me. Heh!
